rainbow baby.description:
Spawns a familiar that follows Isaac around and shoots tears that have random effects similar to other familiars.
The familiar shoots 1.36 times per second.
The familiar can shoot the following types of tears:
• short-range blood tears that deal 6 damage;
• plain red tears that deal 3.5 damage;
• V-pattern double shot tears that deal 3.5 damage each;
• charming purple tears that deal 3.5 damage;
• slowing black tears that deal 3.5 damage;
• spectral tears that deal 3.5 damage;
• long-range homing violet tears that deal 3.5 damage;
• long-range spectral and homing tears that deal 3.5 damage;
• blood tear that deals 4 damage;
• large blood tear that deals 5 damage.

dad s key.description:
Opens all doors in the current room.
It can open:
• any normal door that is closed during combat;
• any door requiring a key/bomb/heart;
• Secret Rooms and Super Secret Rooms;
• Challenge Rooms and Boss Challenge Rooms;
• the door to the Mega Satan arena;
• the Boss Rush door from the inside;
• a mini-boss door from the inside;
• a boss room door from the inside (excluding Mom's room);
• the exit door in Greed Mode.
